    "description": "<strong>加入工匠公会！</strong><br>在 Artisan TD，您将冒险征服混沌群岛。建造高塔迷宫，解救被泰坦巨人侵蚀的魔法战士的灵魂。探索新的塔楼、新的怪物，在 30 张独特的地图中展开冒险。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/7d827e55bf00dfea0514086b8e2d7587.poster.avif?t=1769524569\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/7d827e55bf00dfea0514086b8e2d7587.webm?t=1769524569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/7d827e55bf00dfea0514086b8e2d7587.mp4?t=1769524569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>由一个小型独立团队制作，充满激情，手工平衡。<br>Artisan TD 没有随机性，也没有计算机生成的波形。通过优化您的迷宫，利用地图的地形和特殊地砖。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/abeb9377626763270f1bc455e1382a4d.poster.avif?t=1769524569\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/abeb9377626763270f1bc455e1382a4d.webm?t=1769524569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/abeb9377626763270f1bc455e1382a4d.mp4?t=1769524569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> <br><br>建筑策略和战斗策略会经常更新。用各种行为征服 4 个原始泰坦及其 40 个左右小兵。您还将解锁 10 多座可以升级的新塔楼。<br>此外，一些地图将具有特定的规则集，您必须对其进行调整。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/21c2e9499248f9e9b1b97a461655c8b7.poster.avif?t=1769524569\" width=616 height=308 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/21c2e9499248f9e9b1b97a461655c8b7.webm?t=1769524569\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224640/extras/21c2e9499248f9e9b1b97a461655c8b7.mp4?t=1769524569\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>您可以冒险将农场整合到迷宫中，以管理小型经济体。<br>这款风格化的 PBR 3D 游戏可使用手柄进行游戏，针对大屏幕和 4K 进行了优化。",
